name: Duskfall's Slime Tutorial
description:
Duskfall's Slime Tutorial

If you want to donate towards costs and don't want to subscribe:

https://ko-fi.com/DUSKFALLcrew

If you want to monthly support the EARTH & DUSK media projects and not just AI:

https://www.patreon.com/earthndusk

Discord: https://discord.gg/Da7s8d3KJ7

A highly unintelligent blend of:

  • Beetlejuice: The musical

  • Beetlejuice's one episode in Teen Titans:Go

  • 80s Beetlejuice Cartoon

  • Beetlejuice (The Movie)

  • Alex Brightman & Various Cast Members from the Broadway play.


What should be plainly obvious:

  1. Negative prompts heavy on the "NO TEXT" are imperative.

  2. Photo replication is hilarious but actually scarily darn good.

If you want to yell at us for our weird concepts and come up with better ways of teaching us AND share your AI projects: https://discord.gg/Da7s8d3KJ7

While it's our twitch /media discord, we do want to share the love of AI with peeps so come hang.
